<paragraph blockId="38.[151,1436,325,818]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,323,685,710]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">Bionomics</emphasis>
Adults fly in April. The 
<typeStatus box="[614,712,685,710]" pageId="38" pageNumber="39">holotype</typeStatus>
was swept from the vegetation during early afternoon between light snow flurries. Otherwise biology unknown.
</paragraph>
